  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205960/extras/f3d8778b3d7c3ebecc6dd2ce2c099c94.avif?t=1759502716\" width=1280 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>My Cute Fuhrer</strong> – a satirical anti-war visual novel with “match3”-style gameplay. This game contains no intolerance, no political symbols, and nothing offensive. Only love and mutual understanding. <strong>Make Match3, not war ♥</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the cute and shy <strong>Fuhrer</strong>. She loves painting and dreams of realizing her grand plans. But she has no friends, and nobody takes her seriously. Her greatest dream is to meet someone close and loving… and to take over the world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205960/extras/d39b8c88f24bd6794fa47a6271a0e6db.poster.avif?t=1759502716\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205960/extras/d39b8c88f24bd6794fa47a6271a0e6db.webm?t=1759502716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend the evening with <strong>adorable girls</strong>. Use your charm to melt their <strong>hearts ♥</strong>. Enjoy classic gameplay and a captivating story. <strong>You are a secret agent</strong> – the best there is: devilishly smart, talented, and charming. Your mission is to neutralize the Fuhrer… but can you really do it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205960/extras/0daab2794c4c8e0d86ec5ebeaca4fa2e.webp?t=1759502716\" width=616 height=10 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anti-war love story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute girls in military uniforms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique storyline</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic gameplay: Match3 + visual novel</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lo-fi hip hop soundtrack by G374!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205960/extras/0daab2794c4c8e0d86ec5ebeaca4fa2e.webp?t=1759502716\" width=616 height=10 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205960/extras/f3d8778b3d7c3ebecc6dd2ce2c099c94.avif?t=1759502716\" width=1280 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>My Cute Fuhrer</strong> – a satirical anti-war visual novel with “match3”-style gameplay. This game contains no intolerance, no political symbols, and nothing offensive. Only love and mutual understanding. <strong>Make Match3, not war ♥</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the cute and shy <strong>Fuhrer</strong>. She loves painting and dreams of realizing her grand plans. But she has no friends, and nobody takes her seriously. Her greatest dream is to meet someone close and loving… and to take over the world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205960/extras/d39b8c88f24bd6794fa47a6271a0e6db.poster.avif?t=1759502716\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205960/extras/d39b8c88f24bd6794fa47a6271a0e6db.webm?t=1759502716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend the evening with <strong>adorable girls</strong>. Use your charm to melt their <strong>hearts ♥</strong>. Enjoy classic gameplay and a captivating story. <strong>You are a secret agent</strong> – the best there is: devilishly smart, talented, and charming. Your mission is to neutralize the Fuhrer… but can you really do it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205960/extras/0daab2794c4c8e0d86ec5ebeaca4fa2e.webp?t=1759502716\" width=616 height=10 /